data.description: WELCOME HOME!  Ranch home that offers first floor living.   Interior Features:  3 bedrooms, (master bedroom has a 3/4 bath), formal dining room, large living room with a propane fireplace, spacious remodeled kitchen with a breakfast nook, Lower level has finished area: exercise room.  Exterior features:  Attached one car garage,  plus a rear garage for equipment, deck, fenced in yard, sitting on 1.28 acres
